\pard\qc\b\fs34 ABSTRACT\par
\par
\pard\qj\fs24 This report presents a complete overview of professional training on \b Django Web Development\b0 . The primary objective of the training was to build practical competence in modern web application development using Python and Django. The program covered end-to-end software development practices, including requirement analysis, system design, environment setup, model-view-template architecture, authentication, CRUD operations, REST API development, testing strategies, security hardening, and deployment.\par
\par
The training emphasized hands-on implementation through mini projects and one capstone web application. Key outcomes include improved programming skills, better understanding of software engineering workflows, and readiness to contribute to real-world web development projects. This document summarizes training activities, modules, tools, methodologies, achievements, limitations, and future learning plans.\par
\page

