- Continuous feedback and mentoring\par
\pard\qj\li0 This approach ensured that conceptual understanding translated into practical development skills.\par
\page

\pard\qc\b\fs34 5. TOOLS AND TECHNOLOGY STACK\par
\pard\qj\fs24 The following tools and technologies were used during training:\par
\pard\li720\qj - Programming Language: Python\par
- Framework: Django\par
- Database: SQLite (training), MySQL/PostgreSQL (production concept)\par
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript basics\par
